      • fight

        public void fight()
        Let all the teams in this city fight with each other. The team with largest number of troops will win, and all other teams will disappear. All the resources will be transformed to troops of the remaining team. If teams have the same number of troops, then it is not well defined to decide which team will remain. The remaining troops of a team will be distributed to every user in that team according to their previous troops ratio.
